Game Description:
******************
Alex Hunter thought the case of the missing professor would be an easy paycheck. But his investigation has proven to be anything but simple. What began as a routine open-and-shut affair quickly turned into a race to save a city from a madman who has invented a machine with which he can control the mind of every citizen. As you locate hidden objects, solve puzzles, and open new locations, you'll untie the ingeniously knotted thread designed to keep you from accomplishing your goal: stopping the insanity before it spreads to every person within the lunatic's reach! Set in a beautifully rendered and atmospheric game world, with hours of captivating game time and a storyline inspired by classic detective novels, Alex Hunter: Lord of the Mind will thrill casual game fans looking for their next great adventure!

Game Features:
***************
* Rich, atmospheric world;
* Sherlock Holmes-style story;
* Clever but accessible puzzles;
* Challenging hidden object scenes;
* Animated non-player characters;
* Bonus chapter;
* Extra content

